      • algoSelect

        public void algoSelect(String name)
        The algoSelect function is used to select the algorithm that will be used by the scheduler. The system provides PTMost, T_Most, T_Random and GGA_I algorithms by default.If you need, you can choose them by yourself. If you don't need to select algorithm, the system will provide default algorithm "DefaultAlgo". If you provide new algorithm, please add the algorithm selection to this function.
        指定者:
        algoSelect 在接口中 CrowdKernel
        参数:
        name - Select the needed algorithm and change algorithms in resource's AlgoFactory.
